{"storyMeta":{"storyReviewType":"NONE","storyId":"act19side_level_act19side_03_end","storyGroup":"act19side","storySort":7,"storyDependence":"act19side_level_act19side_03_beg","storyCanShow":1,"storyCode":"DV-3","storyName":"动力装甲","storyPic":null,"storyInfo":"","storyCanEnter":1,"storyTxt":"activities/act19side/level_act19side_03_end","avgTag":"行动后","unLockType":"STAGE_CLEAR","costItemType":"NONE","costItemId":null,"costItemCount":0,"stageCount":1,"requiredStages":[{"stageId":"act19side_03","minState":"PASS","maxState":"COMPLETE"}],"prev":5,"next":7,"characters":["Mechanist","塞雷娅","醉醺醺的男人","斐尔迪南","帕尔维斯","莱茵实验员","莱茵防卫科成员","赫默","桑尼","？？？"]},"lines":[{"type":"header","key":"title_test","skippable":"true","mode":"BLACK_MASK","id":0},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":1},{"type":"stopmusic","id":2},{"type":"dialog","id":3},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/11/Avg_bg_bg_bar_1.png","screenadapt":"showall","id":4},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":5},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$bar_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/act5d0/m_avg_longmenbar_loop.mp3","volume":"0.7","id":6,"musicid":0},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":7},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":8},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_521_1#1$1","id":9},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Mechanist","text":"这熟悉的味道......","id":10,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/db/Avg_avg_npc_521_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Mechanist","text":"可惜工作还没结束，我真有些想念酒精在体内淌过的滋味。","id":11,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/db/Avg_avg_npc_521_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":12},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_521_1#1$1","focus":"-1","id":13},{"type":"decision","options":{"1":{"id":"15","text":"有传言说你的特供饮料是机械润滑油。"},"2":{"id":"21","text":"有传言说你喝多了会踩着凳子表演诗朗诵。"}},"values":[],"id":14},{"type":"predicate","references":["1"],"id":15,"end":20},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_521_1#1$1","id":16},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Mechanist","text":"......一定是煌说的。","id":17,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/db/Avg_avg_npc_521_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Mechanist","text":"她总是感慨为什么关于她的谣言最多，并且经常抱怨我在她测试新武器的对战环节下手太狠。","id":18,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/db/Avg_avg_npc_521_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Mechanist","text":"其实“机油”只是我最喜欢的特调鸡尾酒的名字。","id":19,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/db/Avg_avg_npc_521_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Mechanist","text":"“再来一杯”酒吧的常客都很清楚这一点。","id":20,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/db/Avg_avg_npc_521_1$1.png"},{"type":"predicate","references":["2"],"id":21,"end":25},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_521_1#1$1","id":22},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Mechanist","text":"博士，如果你真的对类似传言感到好奇，下回煌拉你一起喝酒的时候，请不要拒绝。","id":23,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/db/Avg_avg_npc_521_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Mechanist","text":"Logos他们都会在——","id":24,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/db/Avg_avg_npc_521_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Mechanist","text":"到时候，你看到的画面一定会让你忘了这条关于我的传言。","id":25,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/db/Avg_avg_npc_521_1$1.png","end":true},{"type":"useless","references":["1","2"],"id":26},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_521_1#1$1","id":27},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Mechanist","text":"塞雷娅，你要找的人已经到了吗？","id":28,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/db/Avg_avg_npc_521_1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_532_1#1$1","id":29},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塞雷娅","text":"他每天都会在这里待满二十个小时。","id":30,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3c/Avg_avg_npc_532_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塞雷娅","text":"......你好，两杯“特里蒙阳光”。","id":31,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3c/Avg_avg_npc_532_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_521_1#1$1","id":32},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Mechanist","text":"你不像是会在工作时间喝酒的人。","id":33,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/db/Avg_avg_npc_521_1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_532_1#9$1","id":34},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塞雷娅","text":"的确不是。","id":35,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b5/Avg_avg_npc_532_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_532_1#10$1","id":36},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塞雷娅","text":"我不习惯让酒精在任何时候干扰我的大脑。","id":37,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/7c/Avg_avg_npc_532_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_523_1#1$1","id":38},{"type":"dialogue","name":"醉醺醺的男人","text":"你这人还是这么没意思啊，塞雷娅。","id":39,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b0/Avg_avg_npc_523_1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_532_1#1$1","id":40},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塞雷娅","text":"两杯都是你的。","id":41,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3c/Avg_avg_npc_532_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塞雷娅","text":"你最好端稳些，我没打算买第三杯。","id":42,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3c/Avg_avg_npc_532_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_523_1#1$1","id":43},{"type":"dialogue","name":"醉醺醺的男人","text":"啧......怎么，离开莱茵生命以后，你也跟我一样，成了个无家可归的穷鬼？","id":44,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b0/Avg_avg_npc_523_1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_532_1#1$1","id":45},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塞雷娅","text":"我愿意为你支付多少酒钱，取决于你给我的情报有多大价值。","id":46,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3c/Avg_avg_npc_532_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_523_1#1$1","id":47},{"type":"dialogue","name":"醉醺醺的男人","text":"说吧，你想知道什么？","id":48,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b0/Avg_avg_npc_523_1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_532_1#1$1","id":49},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塞雷娅","text":"......看到这试管里的液体了吗？","id":50,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3c/Avg_avg_npc_532_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_523_1#1$1","id":51},{"type":"dialogue","name":"醉醺醺的男人","text":"嘿，我瞧瞧......","id":52,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b0/Avg_avg_npc_523_1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_532_1#1$1","id":53},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塞雷娅","text":"不是用来喝的。","id":54,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3c/Avg_avg_npc_532_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_523_1#1$1","id":55},{"type":"dialogue","name":"醉醺醺的男人","text":"那你就不该来找我。","id":56,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b0/Avg_avg_npc_523_1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_532_1#1$1","id":57},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塞雷娅","text":"给我看看你的右手。","id":58,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3c/Avg_avg_npc_532_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_523_1#1$1","id":59},{"type":"dialogue","name":"醉醺醺的男人","text":"你干什么？","id":60,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b0/Avg_avg_npc_523_1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_532_1#1$1","id":61},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塞雷娅","text":"你是右利手，却在用左手握酒杯。","id":62,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3c/Avg_avg_npc_532_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塞雷娅","text":"这是否说明，你的右小臂仍在因为皮下植入的微型施术单元而疼痛？","id":63,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3c/Avg_avg_npc_532_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_521_1#1$1","id":64},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Mechanist","text":"皮下植入的施术单元？","id":65,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/db/Avg_avg_npc_521_1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_523_1#1$1","id":66},{"type":"dialogue","name":"醉醺醺的男人","text":"......塞雷娅。","id":67,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b0/Avg_avg_npc_523_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"醉醺醺的男人","text":"这男人和边上这个看不清脸的人是什么来路？","id":68,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b0/Avg_avg_npc_523_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"醉醺醺的男人","text":"莱茵工程科，沃尔沃特科钦斯基，还是......那些不能说名字的机构的人？","id":69,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b0/Avg_avg_npc_523_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"醉醺醺的男人","text":"他们是不是改主意了，想让我彻底闭嘴？","id":70,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b0/Avg_avg_npc_523_1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_521_1#1$1","id":71},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Mechanist","text":"我向你保证，我和你口中的这些企业或者组织永远都不会有任何联系。","id":72,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/db/Avg_avg_npc_521_1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_523_1#1$1","id":73},{"type":"dialogue","name":"醉醺醺的男人","text":"保证？口头上的保证还不如我面前的酒来得值钱。","id":74,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b0/Avg_avg_npc_523_1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_521_1#1$1","id":75},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Mechanist","text":"博士，我们也在场的话，他可能不会说实话。","id":76,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/db/Avg_avg_npc_521_1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_523_1#1$1","id":77},{"type":"dialogue","name":"醉醺醺的男人","text":"......问题在你。我不信任你，尤其不信任你这身古怪的打扮。","id":78,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b0/Avg_avg_npc_523_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"醉醺醺的男人","text":"哥伦比亚科技圈子里的精英范儿太浓了，懂吗？","id":79,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b0/Avg_avg_npc_523_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"醉醺醺的男人","text":"戴兜帽的可以留下。你让我有安全感多了。","id":80,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b0/Avg_avg_npc_523_1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_521_1#1$1","id":81},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Mechanist","text":"......","id":82,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/db/Avg_avg_npc_521_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":83},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_521_1#1$1","focus":"-1","id":84},{"type":"decision","options":{"1":{"id":"86","text":"Mechanist，你先休息一会。"},"2":{"id":"86","text":"工作暂停，要不然你也去喝一杯？"}},"values":[],"id":85},{"type":"predicate","references":["1","2"],"id":86,"end":88},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_521_1#1$1","id":87},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Mechanist","text":"行吧，我就在旁边。","id":88,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/db/Avg_avg_npc_521_1$1.png","end":true},{"type":"dialog","id":89},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","id":90},{"type":"character","fadetime":"1.5","id":91},{"type":"delay","time":"2.5","text":"","id":92},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_523_1#1$1","id":93},{"type":"dialogue","name":"醉醺醺的男人","text":"塞雷娅，看在你过去给我买了好几次单的分上，我会给你一个忠告——","id":94,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b0/Avg_avg_npc_523_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"醉醺醺的男人","text":"要是你不想落到跟我一个下场的话，就不要再追查下去。","id":95,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b0/Avg_avg_npc_523_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"醉醺醺的男人","text":"你这试管里的东西，和那批动力甲，它们背后的人都不是你能惹得起的。","id":96,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b0/Avg_avg_npc_523_1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_532_1#1$1","id":97},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塞雷娅","text":"......","id":98,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3c/Avg_avg_npc_532_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_523_1#1$1","id":99},{"type":"dialogue","name":"醉醺醺的男人","text":"是的，连你都不行。","id":100,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b0/Avg_avg_npc_523_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":101},{"type":"dialog","id":102},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":103},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":104},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"1","id":105},{"type":"character","id":106},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_522_1#6$1","name2":"avg_npc_531_1#1$1","id":107},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/49/Avg_bg_29_g9_headquarter.png","screenadapt":"showall","id":108},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":109},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$darkness01_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/beta1_180603/m_dia_darkness01_loop.mp3","volume":"0.7","id":110,"musicid":1},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":111},{"type":"delay","time":"2","text":"","id":112},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_522_1#6$1","name2":"avg_npc_531_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":113},{"type":"dialogue","name":"斐尔迪南","text":"你明不明白你刚才说了什么？","id":114,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/92/Avg_avg_npc_522_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_522_1#6$1","name2":"avg_npc_531_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":115},{"type":"dialogue","name":"帕尔维斯","text":"当然。","id":116,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/91/Avg_avg_npc_531_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"帕尔维斯","text":"是你提醒我的，我还不至于老糊涂。","id":117,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/91/Avg_avg_npc_531_1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_522_1#6$1","name2":"avg_npc_531_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":118},{"type":"dialogue","name":"斐尔迪南","text":"......那是很严重的指控。","id":119,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/92/Avg_avg_npc_522_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_522_1#6$1","name2":"avg_npc_531_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":120},{"type":"dialogue","name":"帕尔维斯","text":"指控？有吗？","id":121,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/91/Avg_avg_npc_531_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"帕尔维斯","text":"哦，你是指缪尔赛思的下落不明与你有关，还是指你想把莱茵生命的总辖头衔据为己有？","id":122,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/91/Avg_avg_npc_531_1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_522_1#6$1","name2":"avg_npc_531_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":123},{"type":"dialogue","name":"斐尔迪南","text":"......","id":124,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/92/Avg_avg_npc_522_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"斐尔迪南","text":"想要威胁我的话，你得拿出点更有说服力的凭据。","id":125,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/92/Avg_avg_npc_522_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_522_1#6$1","name2":"avg_npc_531_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":126},{"type":"dialogue","name":"帕尔维斯","text":"放轻松，我的老朋友。","id":127,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/91/Avg_avg_npc_531_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"帕尔维斯","text":"我们共事多久了？你加入得算晚了，但也有个十年了吧？","id":128,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/91/Avg_avg_npc_531_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"帕尔维斯","text":"你还不了解我吗？我是那种会拿着一沓资料、通讯录音和草拟的法律文书来找老朋友聊天的人吗？","id":129,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/91/Avg_avg_npc_531_1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_522_1#5$1","name2":"avg_npc_531_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":130},{"type":"dialogue","name":"斐尔迪南","text":"你......","id":131,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/46/Avg_avg_npc_522_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_522_1#5$1","name2":"avg_npc_531_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":132},{"type":"dialogue","name":"帕尔维斯","text":"你曾经这样对我，不代表我也会这样对你。","id":133,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/91/Avg_avg_npc_531_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"帕尔维斯","text":"哥伦比亚人喜欢把什么都往谈判桌上摆，可你忘了，我是你口中最喜欢装傻又很阴险的莱塔尼亚老山羊。","id":134,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/91/Avg_avg_npc_531_1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_522_1#6$1","name2":"avg_npc_531_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":135},{"type":"dialogue","name":"斐尔迪南","text":"你究竟想要什么？","id":136,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/92/Avg_avg_npc_522_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_522_1#6$1","name2":"avg_npc_531_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":137},{"type":"dialogue","name":"帕尔维斯","text":"我只是路过，顺便给老朋友鼓鼓劲。","id":138,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/91/Avg_avg_npc_531_1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_522_1#5$1","name2":"avg_npc_531_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":139},{"type":"dialogue","name":"斐尔迪南","text":"我不明白。我以为......你更倾向总辖。","id":140,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/46/Avg_avg_npc_522_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_522_1#5$1","name2":"avg_npc_531_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":141},{"type":"dialogue","name":"帕尔维斯","text":"我们都是搞研究的，难道还不懂这个道理？弄不明白的事情永远比能弄明白的要多，而且这正是做研究的乐趣之一。","id":142,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/91/Avg_avg_npc_531_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"帕尔维斯","text":"你和克丽斯腾其实很相似。你们都太年轻，又太聪明。","id":143,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/91/Avg_avg_npc_531_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"帕尔维斯","text":"一个劲只想往上飞，早晚会把后面跟着的人都累坏。","id":144,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/91/Avg_avg_npc_531_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"帕尔维斯","text":"我只想再安安稳稳做一阵研究，不想跟着一起摔到地上。","id":145,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/91/Avg_avg_npc_531_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"帕尔维斯","text":"莱茵生命在你手上，也许两三年后就被军方和其他大资本撕扯得一干二净，可还不至于明天就粉身碎骨。","id":146,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/91/Avg_avg_npc_531_1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_522_1#6$1","name2":"avg_npc_531_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":147},{"type":"dialogue","name":"斐尔迪南","text":"没想到你对我评价还挺高。","id":148,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/92/Avg_avg_npc_522_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_522_1#6$1","name2":"avg_npc_531_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":149},{"type":"dialogue","name":"帕尔维斯","text":"不过，要动克丽斯腾，你还得先解决我们的防卫科主任。","id":150,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/91/Avg_avg_npc_531_1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_522_1#6$1","name2":"avg_npc_531_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":151},{"type":"dialogue","name":"斐尔迪南","text":"我不记得现在的莱茵生命有防卫科主任。","id":152,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/92/Avg_avg_npc_522_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_522_1#6$1","name2":"avg_npc_531_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":153},{"type":"dialogue","name":"帕尔维斯","text":"瞧你，年纪不大记性却差。","id":154,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/91/Avg_avg_npc_531_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"帕尔维斯","text":"塞雷娅的辞呈，克丽斯腾可至今没有批准。","id":155,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/91/Avg_avg_npc_531_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":156},{"type":"dialog","id":157},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":158},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":159},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"1","id":160},{"type":"character","id":161},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_532_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_523_1#1$1","id":162},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/11/Avg_bg_bg_bar_1.png","screenadapt":"showall","id":163},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":164},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$bar_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/act5d0/m_avg_longmenbar_loop.mp3","volume":"0.7","id":165,"musicid":2},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":166},{"type":"delay","time":"2","text":"","id":167},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_532_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_523_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":168},{"type":"dialogue","name":"醉醺醺的男人","text":"塞雷娅，我其实从来都想不明白你在干什么。","id":169,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b0/Avg_avg_npc_523_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"醉醺醺的男人","text":"洛肯......我是说，我的老东家出事以后，没有人还会把这段经历挂在嘴边。","id":170,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b0/Avg_avg_npc_523_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"醉醺醺的男人","text":"无论知道多少实验的底细，他们都不约而同地选择了撇清关系。","id":171,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b0/Avg_avg_npc_523_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"醉醺醺的男人","text":"这才是聪明人的做法。","id":172,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b0/Avg_avg_npc_523_1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_532_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_523_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":173},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塞雷娅","text":"这是否说明你也是个蠢货？","id":174,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3c/Avg_avg_npc_532_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_532_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_523_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":175},{"type":"dialogue","name":"醉醺醺的男人","text":"哈哈......很好，你说起话来还是这么气人。","id":176,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b0/Avg_avg_npc_523_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"醉醺醺的男人","text":"要是能轻松走掉，我也想走啊。那些人不肯放过我。","id":177,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b0/Avg_avg_npc_523_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"醉醺醺的男人","text":"你总是问我右手还疼不疼，怎么可能不疼？但我要是不废了右手，把自己也变成他们的实验品，他们难道会允许我活到现在？","id":178,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b0/Avg_avg_npc_523_1$1.png"},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"0.3","xstrength":"30","ystrength":"30","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":179},{"type":"dialogue","name":"醉醺醺的男人","text":"我是那个该死的主刀医生！哪怕我压根不知道他们要我植入的是什么！","id":180,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b0/Avg_avg_npc_523_1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_532_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_523_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":181},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塞雷娅","text":"难得你愿意宣泄你的怒火。酒精还没有完全麻痹你的神经。","id":182,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3c/Avg_avg_npc_532_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_532_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_523_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":183},{"type":"dialogue","name":"醉醺醺的男人","text":"而你变了不少，塞雷娅。","id":184,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b0/Avg_avg_npc_523_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"醉醺醺的男人","text":"几年前你第一次来找我的时候，我看得出来，你很愤怒。","id":185,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b0/Avg_avg_npc_523_1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_532_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_523_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":186},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塞雷娅","text":"是吗？","id":187,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3c/Avg_avg_npc_532_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_532_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_523_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":188},{"type":"dialogue","name":"醉醺醺的男人","text":"......虽然从你的表情上看不太出来。","id":189,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b0/Avg_avg_npc_523_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"醉醺醺的男人","text":"但是没错，我能认出来这种愤怒。在得知我当年都参与了什么实验的时候，我也有同样的感受。","id":190,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b0/Avg_avg_npc_523_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"醉醺醺的男人","text":"想要打倒莱茵生命的话，你有的是其他路可以走。","id":191,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b0/Avg_avg_npc_523_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"醉醺醺的男人","text":"你是莱茵的创始人之一，那些觊觎莱茵生命的组织，都会发疯般地邀请你加入。","id":192,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b0/Avg_avg_npc_523_1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_532_1#10$1","name2":"avg_npc_523_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":193},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塞雷娅","text":"一味地针对莱茵生命并不能解决问题。","id":194,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/7c/Avg_avg_npc_532_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塞雷娅","text":"一头死去猛兽的血肉足以喂养出更多可怕的猛兽。洛肯水箱的倒台已经印证了这一点。","id":195,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/7c/Avg_avg_npc_532_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_532_1#10$1","name2":"avg_npc_523_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":196},{"type":"dialogue","name":"醉醺醺的男人","text":"借口。","id":197,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b0/Avg_avg_npc_523_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"醉醺醺的男人","text":"这些年你还在不断地为了莱茵生命奔走，明面上看着是在跟莱茵作对，实际上是在为他们收拾残局。","id":198,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b0/Avg_avg_npc_523_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"醉醺醺的男人","text":"见了你我就知道，那传闻不是假的。","id":199,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b0/Avg_avg_npc_523_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"醉醺醺的男人","text":"——你甚至都愿意为了莱茵生命进监狱。","id":200,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b0/Avg_avg_npc_523_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":201},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_532_1#10$1","name2":"avg_npc_523_1#1$1","focus":"-1","id":202},{"type":"decision","options":{"1":{"id":"204","text":"曼斯菲尔德事件？"},"2":{"id":"204","text":"话说得没错，但听起来好怪......"}},"values":[],"id":203},{"type":"predicate","references":["1","2"],"id":204,"end":224},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_532_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_523_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":205},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塞雷娅","text":"......真相与传闻有出入。","id":206,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3c/Avg_avg_npc_532_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_532_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_523_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":207},{"type":"dialogue","name":"醉醺醺的男人","text":"海德兄弟倒了，这让你们莱茵那个能量科主任挺头疼对吧？","id":208,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b0/Avg_avg_npc_523_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"醉醺醺的男人","text":"少了基础材料供应商，新的实验基地审批频频受阻，我听说他损失了好几个大订单。","id":209,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b0/Avg_avg_npc_523_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"醉醺醺的男人","text":"不管他在做什么实验，进度都不得不放缓。","id":210,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b0/Avg_avg_npc_523_1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_532_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_523_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":211},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塞雷娅","text":"最终把海德兄弟送进监狱的人可不是我。","id":212,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3c/Avg_avg_npc_532_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_523_1#1$1","id":213},{"type":"musicvolume","volume":"0.2","fadetime":"1","id":214},{"type":"dialogue","name":"醉醺醺的男人","text":"你出的力可不会少。","id":215,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b0/Avg_avg_npc_523_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"醉醺醺的男人","text":"规矩我都懂，海德兄弟进了监狱，地方检察官肯定会想拿他们钓出更大的鳞。","id":216,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b0/Avg_avg_npc_523_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"醉醺醺的男人","text":"为什么新闻里没有莱茵的影子？为什么莱茵生命总能从这些事件中脱身？","id":217,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b0/Avg_avg_npc_523_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"醉醺醺的男人","text":"事实就是，你一路追着纠正莱茵犯下的所有错。","id":218,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b0/Avg_avg_npc_523_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"醉醺醺的男人","text":"要不然你也不会来找我......","id":219,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b0/Avg_avg_npc_523_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"醉醺醺的男人","text":"你急着确认这份试剂到底和莱茵生命有没有关系。","id":220,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b0/Avg_avg_npc_523_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"醉醺醺的男人","text":"在你内心深处，你还是莱茵防卫科的主任。你仍然把收拾莱茵生命折腾出来的烂摊子视为己任。","id":221,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b0/Avg_avg_npc_523_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"醉醺醺的男人","text":"莱茵生命里仍然有你不能舍弃的东西。不管那是一个人，还是什么扯淡情怀......","id":222,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b0/Avg_avg_npc_523_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"醉醺醺的男人","text":"哈哈，塞雷娅，我发现了，你也会感情用事！","id":223,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b0/Avg_avg_npc_523_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"醉醺醺的男人","text":"到头来，我们都只是血肉之躯。","id":224,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b0/Avg_avg_npc_523_1$1.png","end":true},{"type":"dialog","id":225},{"type":"dialog","id":226},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":227},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":228},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"1","id":229},{"type":"character","id":230},{"type":"cameraeffect","effect":"Grayscale","amount":"0.8","keep":"true","id":231},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b1/Avg_bg_29_g4_corridor.png","screenadapt":"showall","id":232},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":233},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":234},{"type":"delay","time":"2","text":"","id":235},{"type":"playsound","key":"$firestorm","volume":"1","text":"","id":236},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"5","xstrength":"50","ystrength":"50","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":237},{"type":"delay","time":"6.5","text":"","id":238},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_530_1#1$1","id":239},{"type":"dialogue","name":"莱茵实验员","text":"失控了......实验体彻底失去控制！","id":240,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/55/Avg_avg_npc_530_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"莱茵实验员","text":"束缚装置失效！","id":241,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/55/Avg_avg_npc_530_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"莱茵实验员","text":"实验体意识无法检测......镇定剂注射失败！","id":242,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/55/Avg_avg_npc_530_1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_528_1#1$1","id":243},{"type":"dialogue","name":"莱茵防卫科成员","text":"实验体正在大规模施放源石技艺！","id":244,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/7d/Avg_avg_npc_528_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":245},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"255","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.07","block":"true","id":246},{"type":"playsound","key":"$e_atk_aim","volume":"1","text":"","id":247},{"type":"blocker","a":"0.5","r":"255","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.07","block":"true","id":248},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"255","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.07","block":"true","id":249},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"0.6","xstrength":"30","ystrength":"30","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"true","id":250},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":251},{"type":"delay","time":"1","text":"","id":252},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_528_1#1$1","id":253},{"type":"dialogue","name":"莱茵防卫科成员","text":"怪物......巨型生物......","id":254,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/7d/Avg_avg_npc_528_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"莱茵防卫科成员","text":"不，火焰具象化......","id":255,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/7d/Avg_avg_npc_528_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"莱茵防卫科成员","text":"......立刻通知主任！","id":256,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/7d/Avg_avg_npc_528_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":257},{"type":"playsound","key":"$rungeneral","id":258},{"type":"character","fadetime":"1.5","id":259},{"type":"delay","time":"2.5","text":"","id":260},{"type":"dialog","id":261},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":262},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":263},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":264},{"type":"blocker","a":"0.3","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":265},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":266},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","id":267},{"type":"character","name":"avg_108_silent_1#6$1","fadetime":"1.5","id":268},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":269},{"type":"character","name":"avg_108_silent_1#6$1","id":270},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"火......好大的火......咳咳咳......","id":271,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/65/Avg_avg_108_silent_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"伊芙利特在哪里......","id":272,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/65/Avg_avg_108_silent_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_108_silent_1#5$1","id":273},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"伊芙利特——！","id":274,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3a/Avg_avg_108_silent_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":275},{"type":"character","id":276},{"type":"delay","time":"0.8","id":277},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","id":278},{"type":"character","name":"avg_202_demkni_1#1$1","fadetime":"1.5","id":279},{"type":"delay","time":"3","id":280},{"type":"character","name":"avg_108_silent_1#5$1","id":281},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"塞雷娅......？！","id":282,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3a/Avg_avg_108_silent_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":283},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":284},{"type":"character","id":285},{"type":"text","text":"火光填满了整条走廊，她却感觉不到热。","id":286},{"type":"text","text":"因为注视着她的瓦伊凡眼神比盾牌还硬，比刀刃更冷。","id":287},{"type":"text","text":"她看不懂那里面蕴含的情绪。","id":288},{"type":"text","text":"她至今都不敢确信，自己在看着瓦伊凡眼睛的时候，看到的究竟是什么。","id":289},{"type":"dialog","id":290},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":291},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"1","id":292},{"type":"character","id":293},{"type":"cameraeffect","effect":"Grayscale","fadetime":"0","amount":"0","block":"true","id":294},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b1/Avg_bg_29_g4_corridor.png","screenadapt":"showall","id":295},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":296},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$drift_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/act9d0d0/m_avg_drift_loop.mp3","volume":"0.6","id":297,"musicid":3},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":298},{"type":"delay","time":"2","text":"","id":299},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_535_1#7$1","id":300},{"type":"dialogue","name":"桑尼","text":"赫默医生，您没事吧？","id":301,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/54/Avg_avg_npc_535_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_108_silent_1#6$1","id":302},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"我......","id":303,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/65/Avg_avg_108_silent_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_535_1#8$1","id":304},{"type":"dialogue","name":"桑尼","text":"您一定是累了。","id":305,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/df/Avg_avg_npc_535_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"桑尼","text":"这一路上，您都在照顾摩尔医生，还有我们。","id":306,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/df/Avg_avg_npc_535_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_535_1#4$1","id":307},{"type":"dialogue","name":"桑尼","text":"之前是我反应过激，差点伤到您，我很抱歉。","id":308,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/60/Avg_avg_npc_535_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_535_1#8$1","id":309},{"type":"dialogue","name":"桑尼","text":"罗德岛与莱茵生命不一样，您和格雷伊先生善待我们却不求回报。","id":310,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/df/Avg_avg_npc_535_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_108_silent_1#10$1","id":311},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"不求回报......？","id":312,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/2d/Avg_avg_108_silent_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"桑尼先生，我不是没有犯过错。","id":313,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/2d/Avg_avg_108_silent_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_108_silent_1#6$1","id":314},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"我也是莱茵生命的研究员。我主导过的实验，差点害死一个街区的人......","id":315,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/65/Avg_avg_108_silent_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_535_1#7$1","id":316},{"type":"dialogue","name":"桑尼","text":"啊？","id":317,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/54/Avg_avg_npc_535_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_108_silent_1#10$1","id":318},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"而且，有一个孩子，她非常依赖我，几乎把我当成了她的亲人。","id":319,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/2d/Avg_avg_108_silent_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"她就是那个实验的受试者。","id":320,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/2d/Avg_avg_108_silent_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_535_1#8$1","id":321},{"type":"dialogue","name":"桑尼","text":"那她现在......","id":322,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/df/Avg_avg_npc_535_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_108_silent_1#10$1","id":323},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"她还活着。","id":324,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/2d/Avg_avg_108_silent_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"只是活着而已......这么多年，我倾尽全力，依然没法让她回归正常的生活......","id":325,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/2d/Avg_avg_108_silent_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"我甚至连阻止情况恶化都做不到。","id":326,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/2d/Avg_avg_108_silent_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_535_1#8$1","id":327},{"type":"dialogue","name":"桑尼","text":"您也不要太自责，我相信您从来没想过要害她。","id":328,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/df/Avg_avg_npc_535_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_108_silent_1#10$1","id":329},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"哈......哈哈......","id":330,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/2d/Avg_avg_108_silent_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"有趣的是，我过去也这么安慰过自己。","id":331,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/2d/Avg_avg_108_silent_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_108_silent_1#6$1","id":332},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"我原本并不知道——真正可恨的是其他人。","id":333,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/65/Avg_avg_108_silent_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"可真的仅仅是这样吗？","id":334,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/65/Avg_avg_108_silent_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":335},{"type":"text","text":"作为实验实施阶段的第一负责人，我在一开始，难道就一点都没有察觉到这项研究可能的风险？","id":336},{"type":"text","text":"答案显而易见。","id":337},{"type":"character","name":"avg_108_silent_1#10$1","id":338},{"type":"text","text":"要么是我被眼前即将能达成的开创性的成就蒙蔽了视线......","id":339},{"type":"text","text":"要么是我作为研究者远不及我自以为的那般优秀。","id":340},{"type":"text","text":"要承认这一点，的确要比恨别人更难。","id":341},{"type":"character","name":"avg_108_silent_1#10$1","id":342},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"或许，我真正无法原谅的人是......","id":343,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/2d/Avg_avg_108_silent_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"......","id":344,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/2d/Avg_avg_108_silent_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_535_1#7$1","id":345},{"type":"dialogue","name":"桑尼","text":"没想到您还有这样的过去。","id":346,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/54/Avg_avg_npc_535_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_108_silent_1#10$1","id":347},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"这不仅仅是我的过去，也是我来到这个基地的原因。","id":348,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/2d/Avg_avg_108_silent_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_535_1#1$1","id":349},{"type":"dialogue","name":"桑尼","text":"您不是为了救您的朋友吗？","id":350,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/96/Avg_avg_npc_535_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_108_silent_1#10$1","id":351},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"当然，我要救乔伊丝。","id":352,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/2d/Avg_avg_108_silent_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_108_silent_1#8$1","id":353},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"但我也要救你们，救埃琳娜，救弗兰克斯主任。","id":354,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/ac/Avg_avg_108_silent_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_108_silent_1#7$1","id":355},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"在事情走向无可挽回之前，我要试试看阻止灾难发生。","id":356,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/08/Avg_avg_108_silent_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_535_1#7$1","id":357},{"type":"dialogue","name":"桑尼","text":"......您相信我的说辞？","id":358,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/54/Avg_avg_npc_535_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_108_silent_1#7$1","id":359},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"我说过，我相信真相，相信自己亲眼所见。","id":360,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/08/Avg_avg_108_silent_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"我刚刚才想起来，类似场景我曾经见过。","id":361,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/08/Avg_avg_108_silent_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"那些追着我们跑的银色物体——它们很像源石技艺失控的产物。","id":362,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/08/Avg_avg_108_silent_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":363},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":364},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":365},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"1","id":366},{"type":"character","id":367},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_522_1#6$1","name2":"avg_npc_531_1#1$1","id":368},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/49/Avg_bg_29_g9_headquarter.png","screenadapt":"showall","id":369},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":370},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$darkness01_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/beta1_180603/m_dia_darkness01_loop.mp3","volume":"0.7","id":371,"musicid":4},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":372},{"type":"delay","time":"2","text":"","id":373},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_522_1#6$1","name2":"avg_npc_531_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":374},{"type":"dialogue","name":"帕尔维斯","text":"对了，我让本给你送了点东西，眼下应该放在你办公桌上了。","id":375,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/91/Avg_avg_npc_531_1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_522_1#7$1","name2":"avg_npc_531_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":376},{"type":"dialogue","name":"斐尔迪南","text":"本？","id":377,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/9c/Avg_avg_npc_522_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_522_1#7$1","name2":"avg_npc_531_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":378},{"type":"dialogue","name":"帕尔维斯","text":"你又忘了？你之前刚让他来找我喝茶。那小子磕磕巴巴地说了一大堆话，差点把我的茶包库存喝空。","id":379,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/91/Avg_avg_npc_531_1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_522_1#7$1","name2":"avg_npc_531_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":380},{"type":"dialogue","name":"斐尔迪南","text":"我不记得你欠我什么东西。","id":381,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/9c/Avg_avg_npc_522_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_522_1#7$1","name2":"avg_npc_531_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":382},{"type":"dialogue","name":"帕尔维斯","text":"哦？我的嵌合生命体实验刚结束的时候，你可不是这么说的。","id":383,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/91/Avg_avg_npc_531_1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_522_1#6$1","name2":"avg_npc_531_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":384},{"type":"dialogue","name":"斐尔迪南","text":"......炎魔实验。","id":385,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/92/Avg_avg_npc_522_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_522_1#6$1","name2":"avg_npc_531_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":386},{"type":"dialogue","name":"帕尔维斯","text":"很高兴你还记得。","id":387,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/91/Avg_avg_npc_531_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"帕尔维斯","text":"在那个实验的最终阶段，我的学生用上了她自制的神经麻醉剂。","id":388,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/91/Avg_avg_npc_531_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"帕尔维斯","text":"麻醉剂产生了令人震惊的效果——","id":389,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/91/Avg_avg_npc_531_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"帕尔维斯","text":"唉，赫默真是个聪明的孩子，我又开始想她了。","id":390,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/91/Avg_avg_npc_531_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"帕尔维斯","text":"在我的实验被叫停之后，我又检查了之前得到的几个数据，发现这并不是巧合。","id":391,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/91/Avg_avg_npc_531_1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_522_1#6$1","name2":"avg_npc_531_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":392},{"type":"dialogue","name":"斐尔迪南","text":"什么数据？","id":393,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/92/Avg_avg_npc_522_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_522_1#6$1","name2":"avg_npc_531_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":394},{"type":"dialogue","name":"帕尔维斯","text":"偶尔会翻找废品的人可不止你一个。","id":395,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/91/Avg_avg_npc_531_1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_522_1#6$1","name2":"avg_npc_531_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":396},{"type":"dialogue","name":"斐尔迪南","text":"你是说洛肯水箱？那些资料我明明都......","id":397,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/92/Avg_avg_npc_522_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_522_1#6$1","name2":"avg_npc_531_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":398},{"type":"dialogue","name":"帕尔维斯","text":"手续方面的事，你就不用跟我计较了吧？","id":399,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/91/Avg_avg_npc_531_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"帕尔维斯","text":"洛肯·威廉姆斯真是个天才，看完他的数据，我才意识到，我在实验思路上走了一点小小的弯路。","id":400,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/91/Avg_avg_npc_531_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"帕尔维斯","text":"那时候，我想方设法要提升实验体的细胞活性，好让她更好地与嵌入碎片里的能量同调——","id":401,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/91/Avg_avg_npc_531_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"帕尔维斯","text":"谁能想到，抑制实验体的神经反应才是正确的做法？","id":402,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/91/Avg_avg_npc_531_1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_522_1#6$1","name2":"avg_npc_531_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":403},{"type":"dialogue","name":"斐尔迪南","text":"抑制......？","id":404,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/92/Avg_avg_npc_522_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_522_1#6$1","name2":"avg_npc_531_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":405},{"type":"dialogue","name":"帕尔维斯","text":"基于以上猜想，我对你的公式做出了一些小小的改动。","id":406,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/91/Avg_avg_npc_531_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"帕尔维斯","text":"希望你别介意我的自作主张。","id":407,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/91/Avg_avg_npc_531_1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_522_1#6$1","name2":"avg_npc_531_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":408},{"type":"dialogue","name":"斐尔迪南","text":"......你真的很狡猾，老山羊。","id":409,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/92/Avg_avg_npc_522_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_522_1#6$1","name2":"avg_npc_531_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":410},{"type":"dialogue","name":"帕尔维斯","text":"这么咬牙切齿做什么？我只是在你提出来之前，主动把礼物送上门而已。","id":411,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/91/Avg_avg_npc_531_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"帕尔维斯","text":"只不过是少了一个对付我的把柄，有这么可惜吗？","id":412,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/91/Avg_avg_npc_531_1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_522_1#6$1","name2":"avg_npc_531_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":413},{"type":"dialogue","name":"斐尔迪南","text":"它最好对我的实验有帮助。","id":414,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/92/Avg_avg_npc_522_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_522_1#6$1","name2":"avg_npc_531_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":415},{"type":"dialogue","name":"帕尔维斯","text":"我保证你会感到惊喜。","id":416,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/91/Avg_avg_npc_531_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"帕尔维斯","text":"对了，要是你成功了，能不能把缪尔赛思欠我的十盒黑豆茶补上？","id":417,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/91/Avg_avg_npc_531_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"帕尔维斯","text":"没有我的公式的话，那个赌我本来能打赢的。","id":418,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/91/Avg_avg_npc_531_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":419},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":420},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":421},{"type":"character","id":422},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_532_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_523_1#1$1","id":423},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/11/Avg_bg_bg_bar_1.png","screenadapt":"showall","id":424},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":425},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":426},{"type":"delay","time":"2","text":"","id":427},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_532_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_523_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":428},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塞雷娅","text":"言归正传吧。","id":429,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3c/Avg_avg_npc_532_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塞雷娅","text":"——这试剂。","id":430,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3c/Avg_avg_npc_532_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_532_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_523_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":431},{"type":"dialogue","name":"醉醺醺的男人","text":"你拿出来的时候我就闻过了。","id":432,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b0/Avg_avg_npc_523_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"醉醺醺的男人","text":"是的，一模一样的味道。","id":433,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b0/Avg_avg_npc_523_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"醉醺醺的男人","text":"哈哈......死在我的手术台上的幽魂......他们又回来了。","id":434,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b0/Avg_avg_npc_523_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"醉醺醺的男人","text":"浓度更高，数量更多......","id":435,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b0/Avg_avg_npc_523_1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_532_1#8$1","name2":"avg_npc_523_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":436},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塞雷娅","text":"谁......？","id":437,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f7/Avg_avg_npc_532_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_532_1#8$1","name2":"avg_npc_523_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":438},{"type":"dialogue","name":"醉醺醺的男人","text":"你问是谁？","id":439,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b0/Avg_avg_npc_523_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"醉醺醺的男人","text":"谁从洛肯水箱的废墟中扒出了最多遗产？","id":440,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b0/Avg_avg_npc_523_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"醉醺醺的男人","text":"你该回家看看了，塞雷娅。","id":441,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b0/Avg_avg_npc_523_1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_532_1#8$1","name2":"avg_npc_523_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":442},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塞雷娅","text":"......莱茵生命。","id":443,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f7/Avg_avg_npc_532_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_532_1#8$1","name2":"avg_npc_523_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":444},{"type":"dialogue","name":"醉醺醺的男人","text":"看啊，你明明知道答案。","id":445,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b0/Avg_avg_npc_523_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"醉醺醺的男人","text":"你早就见过“锡人”了，就是他帮你找到了我。","id":446,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b0/Avg_avg_npc_523_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"醉醺醺的男人","text":"“炎魔”实验的最大资助者是谁？洛肯水箱的投资人又是谁？","id":447,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b0/Avg_avg_npc_523_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"醉醺醺的男人","text":"谁有能力在几乎同一时间雇佣多家顶尖实验室开展近似的研究？","id":448,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b0/Avg_avg_npc_523_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"醉醺醺的男人","text":"几家实验室平时会为某个微不足道的专利打得头破血流，能让他们坐在一起共享研究资料的，是多么无法拒绝的订单？","id":449,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b0/Avg_avg_npc_523_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"醉醺醺的男人","text":"还有......","id":450,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b0/Avg_avg_npc_523_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"醉醺醺的男人","text":"那些活下来的实验个体，在被送出哥伦比亚之前，都经过谁的手？","id":451,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b0/Avg_avg_npc_523_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":452},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_532_1#8$1","name2":"avg_npc_523_1#1$1","focus":"-1","id":453},{"type":"decision","options":{"1":{"id":"455","text":"你是说......"}},"values":[],"id":454},{"type":"predicate","references":["1"],"id":455,"end":true},{"type":"dialog","id":456},{"type":"character","id":457},{"type":"delay","time":"0.51","id":458},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"1","id":459},{"type":"dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"哎呀，几位真是相谈甚欢。","id":460},{"type":"dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"看来我有些来晚了呢。","id":461},{"type":"dialog","id":462},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":463},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":464},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"1","id":465},{"type":"character","id":466},{"type":"image","id":467}],"characters":["Mechanist","塞雷娅","醉醺醺的男人","斐尔迪南","帕尔维斯","莱茵实验员","莱茵防卫科成员","赫默","桑尼","？？？"]}